tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE student_demographics (
    student_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    first_name VARCHAR(50),
    last_name VARCHAR(50),
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    enrollment_status VARCHAR(20)
)

CREATE TABLE enrollment_numbers (
    enrollment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    student_id INT,
    enrollment_date DATE,
    program_name VARCHAR(50),
    enrollment_status VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE student_demographics (
    student_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    first_name STRING,
    last_name STRING,
    birthdate DATE,
    gender STRING
);

CREATE TABLE students (
    student_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    student_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    gender CHAR(1),
    date_of_birth DATE,
    enrollment_status VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE enrollments (
    enrollment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    student_id INT,
    course_id INT,
    enrollment_date DATE,
    grade VARCHAR(2)
);

CREATE TABLE demographics (
    demographic_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    student_id INT,
    ethnicity VARCHAR(50),
    hometown VARCHAR(50),
    family_income DECIMAL(10, 2)
);

CREATE TABLE Students (
    student_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    first_name VARCHAR(50),
    last_name VARCHAR(50),
    birthdate DATE,
    gender VARCHAR(10)
);
